{"tid":265681,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"[求解答］手提電腦顯示卡好似壞左？","createTime":"2017-05-31T22:39:24.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-02T04:05:13.000Z","uid":109474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"05d0173106f9f18ce8658bd2a1c95ee1c1d4495e","tid":265681,"uid":109474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T22:39:24.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n<br />\n小弟13年入手買左部手提電腦 內置係有張 nvidia gt630<br />\n但之後15年有次過熱電源插頭位燒溶左拎左去整<br />\n整完就發覺部電腦好似無之前咁順<br />\n打機會間唔中跳fps 會疾下機咁<br />\n<br />\n我頭先開個 dxdiag 係display個度唔見左個gt630<br />\n淨係見到 intel hd graphic 4000<br />\n<br />\n想問一下<br />\n<br />\nIntel hd graphic 4000 係咪 i7 內置 display?<br />\n我可以點check 我張 gt630 係壞左定係間黑店換走左 ?<br />\n<br />\n跪求高手賜教<br />\n我淨係想打lol唔跳ping唔疾<br />\n1TB hd 8gb ram i7-3630QM"},{"pid":"9780275ed7c8e6af069b447da361d69a35576065","tid":265681,"uid":109474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T22:46:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c36aea5e8ab088f137a728543009ef89111dc396","tid":265681,"uid":7758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T22:59:12.000Z","msg":"630照計係換唔走<br />\n可能真係壞display card"},{"pid":"e9b66a0f143c3efe846d27b6ea236edc0ba91cd3","tid":265681,"uid":109474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T23:03:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>630照計係換唔走<br />\n可能真係壞display card</blockquote><br />\n過左保養有無得整？"},{"pid":"659e52dadb907a7abd824c8918e17bd3b41a5ce9","tid":265681,"uid":45440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T23:06:41.000Z","msg":"電池火牛要同時插先用到gt630"},{"pid":"c8c17c56b58482d2abd11b2c357cec1ddd99bc44","tid":265681,"uid":109474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T23:25:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>電池火牛要同時插先用到gt630</blockquote><br />\n我有插到呀<br />\n但點先check到有無壞？"},{